data.description: Penn cove spectacular & rare no bank waterfront property home on 3 tax parcels w/over 180 ft of private waterfront in coveted Penn Cove. 3rd Lot is buildable with much of the prelim work already done. Sitting just outside of town limits, there are no nightly rental restrictions for this marvelous property that is both tranquil & serene w/amazing views of Mt. Baker and Penn Cove! Make this your private home, part time get away or your newest investment. This home has been beautifully transformed into a modern retreat with upscale cabinetry and appliances, luxurious bathrooms and of course breathtaking views. Entertain from your expansive deck overlooking the newly poured stamped patio and fire pit, or sip coffee.1yr home warranty included.
